enhanced-privacy: Choosing Enhanced Privacy will result in slower transaction speeds. However, this option allows you to use the Resistance coin (RES) as an intermediary mixer that utilizes zero-knowledge proofs to give any coin traded on the DEX privacy elements — even if such benefits didn’t exist before.
